---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import imgHero from "../assets/img-hero.svg";
---

<section
  class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row
         items-center justify-between gap-12 lg:gap-16 px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 pt-12 sm:pt-16 lg:pt-8"
>
  <!-- Texto -->
  <article
    class="text-white flex flex-col gap-6 items-start
            pt-0 pb-16 sm:pt-0 sm:pb-20 lg:py-20 text-center lg:text-left w-full lg:w-1/2"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <span
        class="text-emerald-300 font-semibold tracking-wider text-sm uppercase bg-emerald-900/40 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full w-fit mx-auto lg:mx-0 border border-emerald-500/40 backdrop-blur-sm"
      >
        Tu socio tecnológico integral
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl
               font-extrabold max-w-2xl leading-tight tracking-tight text-white"
      >
        Impulsamos tu Negocio con <span
          class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-emerald-200 to-cyan-200"
          >Soluciones Digitales</span
        > a Medida
      </h1>
    </div>

    <p
      class="text-base sm:text-lg text-neutral-100 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-light mx-auto lg:mx-0 opacity-90"
    >
      En Ganex, fusionamos creatividad y tecnología para desarrollar sitios web,
      aplicaciones móviles y estrategias de marketing que no solo existen, sino
      que <strong>venden y conectan</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto mt-2">
      <a
        href="#servicios"
        class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-[#FF8A00] text-base font-bold
               rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-300
               hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-orange-50 w-full sm:w-auto"
      >
        Explorar Servicios
      </a>
      <a
        href="#soporte"
        class="px-8 py-3.5 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/30 text-white text-base
               rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300
               hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-white/20 w-full sm:w-auto"
      >
        Agendar Cita
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Imagen -->
  <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end relative">
    <div
      class="absolute -inset-10 bg-linear-to-tr from-orange-400/30 to-purple-500/30 rounded-full blur-[80px] -z-10 animate-pulse-slow"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative w-full max-w-lg lg:max-w-xl transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500"
    >
      <Image
        src={imgHero}
        alt="Estrategia digital y desarrollo web con Ganex"
        width={800}
        height={600}
        class="w-full h-auto drop-shadow-2xl animate-float"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes float {
    0% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-15px);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
  }
  .animate-float {
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse 8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
  }
</style>
